{
  "texts": [
    "For \"Contextualization\" and \"Appropriateness\", we also ask the annotators to motivate the negative judgments with the explanations proposed in the original protocol.",
    "We present the explanations and related results in §4.3.",
    "We recruited 75 annotators on the Prolific platform foot_2, and we assigned 5 dialogues to each annotator.",
    "After performing quality control, we approved 65 annotators with a compensation of 9.00£/hour (marked as good on the Prolific platform).",
    "Due to the large number of responses, each annotator evaluated a different set of model responses for a given dialogue."
  ]
}